last_episode_to_air.name: Emotional Consequences of Broadcast Television
last_episode_to_air.overview: The former study group's future — and friendships — are put to a test when one chapter of their lives closes and a new one begins.

name: Community
overview: Follow the lives of a group of students at what is possibly the world’s worst community college in the fictional locale of Greendale, Colorado.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: After his bachelor's degree is revoked, lawyer Jeff Winger returns to community college, where he forms a study group with a few oddballs.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: The misfits of Greendale Community College return for more wacky lessons in love, life and friendship in the second season of this ensemble sitcom.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: The motley gang of eccentrics anchored by disbarred lawyer Jeff Winger is back for another season of learning in this sardonic comedy series.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Greendale Community College continues to attract an odd assortment of intellectual "seekers" in the fourth season of this sardonic sitcom.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: Attorney Jeff Winger and his wacky study group are assailed by new academic and life challenges in the fifth season of this mischievous sitcom.

seasons.name: Season 6
seasons.overview: Greendale's best worst former study group learns lessons in life and the chemistry of weirdness as it graduates to a momentous ending. Maybe.

tagline: Mastering the B.S. degree at community college.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: When the legitimacy of his degree is challenged, lawyer Jeff Winger must return to school, where he meets a clan of misfit community college students.

episodes.name: Spanish 101
episodes.overview: While Jeff looks to use a Spanish class assignment to get close to Britta, Pierce has something altogether different in mind.

episodes.name: Introduction to Film
episodes.overview: Jeff struggles to get a good grade, and Britta's offer to bankroll his film class exposes a rift between Abed and his angry father.

episodes.name: Social Psychology
episodes.overview: As Annie recruits Abed and Troy for a psychology class experiment, Jeff and Shirley bond over their mutual fondness for gossip.

episodes.name: Advanced Criminal Law
episodes.overview: As Pierce volunteers to compose a new school song, a cheating episode in Spanish class leaves Jeff defending Britta before a disciplinary tribunal.

episodes.name: Football, Feminism and You
episodes.overview: Annie's dream of being the ex-football star's girlfriend is in jeopardy when Jeff is blackmailed into getting Troy to join Greendale's football team.

episodes.name: Introduction to Statistics
episodes.overview: Jeff sets his sights on an attractive professor, and Annie looks to boost her social standing by hosting a Day of the Dead party.

episodes.name: Home Economics
episodes.overview: Jeff is forced out of his condo and into Abed's dorm room, and Annie looks to get Troy's attention by helping him plan a romantic picnic.

episodes.name: Debate 109
episodes.overview: As Jeff is drafted to help lead Greendale's debate team against the formidable City College, Abed's film-class projects appear to predict the future.

episodes.name: Environmental Science
episodes.overview: Faced with an unreasonable amount of Spanish homework, Jeff's efforts to handle Señor Chang manage to help him, but not the rest of the class.

episodes.name: The Politics of Human Sexuality
episodes.overview: With his high-price "escort" girlfriend on his arm, Pierce pressures Jeff into asking Dean Pelton's airhead secretary to double date at the STD Fair.

episodes.name: Comparative Religion
episodes.overview: Shirley's plans for a holiday party are in jeopardy when Jeff is drawn into a fight with a campus bully.

episodes.name: Investigative Journalism
episodes.overview: Jeff accepts an invitation to be the editor of the school paper as he and his friends fend off an interloper who wants to join their study group.

episodes.name: Interpretive Dance
episodes.overview: As Jeff and Prof. Slater try to keep their student-teacher romance under wraps, Britta and Troy tell everyone about their shared passion for dance.

episodes.name: Romantic Expressionism
episodes.overview: Jeff and Britta team up to derail Annie's fledgling romance with Greendale's resident hippie singer-songwriter, Vaughn.

episodes.name: Communication Studies
episodes.overview: As Valentine's Day finds Jeff struggling with his feelings for Britta and Professor Slater, Pierce and Troy are wrongly blamed for a prank.

episodes.name: Physical Education
episodes.overview: The study group helps Abed land a date with a girl, and Jeff squares off with a P.E. coach who insists that he wear gym shorts to a billiards class.

episodes.name: Basic Genealogy
episodes.overview: As Family Day lands Jeff in the middle of an affair with Pierce's sexy ex-stepdaughter, Shirley's unruly sons help liberate Abed's Afghani cousin.

episodes.name: Beginner Pottery
episodes.overview: A pottery class he takes for an easy A reveals Jeff's deep-seated need to succeed.

episodes.name: The Science of Illusion
episodes.overview: When her April Fools' Day prank inadvertently sends a human cadaver out the anatomy lab window, Britta looks to place the blame on Jeff.

episodes.name: Contemporary American Poultry
episodes.overview: A scheme to replace a corrupt cafeteria employee transforms the study group into a criminal gang run by a power-hungry Abed.

episodes.name: The Art of Discourse
episodes.overview: While a tasteless prank ends with Pierce being tossed out of the group, Britta and Jeff are forced to team up against some teen newcomers at school.

episodes.name: Modern Warfare
episodes.overview: The first prize of priority registration engulfs Greendale Community College in a Spring Fling paintball war.

episodes.name: English as a Second Language
episodes.overview: On the eve of an important final exam in Spanish, everyone's grades are jeopardized when it is discovered that Señor Chang has a damaging secret.

episodes.name: Pascal's Triangle Revisited
episodes.overview: As the end of the school year finds Jeff at the apex of a romantic triangle, Annie ponders moving away with her hacky sack-playing boyfriend.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: After his bachelor's degree is revoked, lawyer Jeff Winger returns to community college, where he forms a study group with a few oddballs.

episodes.name: Anthropology 101
episodes.overview: When the semester starts, Jeff is stunned that his rejection of Britta has made her a campus star; Chang wants to be accepted into the study group.

episodes.name: Accounting for Lawyers
episodes.overview: When an old friend from Jeff's past appears unexpectedly, his friends discover that he was the one responsible for Jeff's disbarment.

episodes.name: The Psychology of Letting Go
episodes.overview: A death provokes a fierce debate about Pierce's religious beliefs. Britta and Annie are at odds over tactics in the Gulf oil spill fund-raising drive.

episodes.name: Basic Rocket Science
episodes.overview: Jeff and the group must salvage an aging museum exhibit that Dean Pelton wants as the centerpiece of Greendale's proposed aerospace training program.

episodes.name: Messianic Myths and Ancient Peoples
episodes.overview: Shirley and Abed are at odds over his plan to direct and star in his own epic religious film.

episodes.name: Epidemiology
episodes.overview: Dean Pelton's army surplus party food sparks an outbreak of zombie-ism at the Greendale Halloween party.

episodes.name: Aerodynamics of Gender
episodes.overview: Abed endears himself to the girls after he offers to take down their enemies on campus; Jeff and Troy stumble onto a groundskeeper's secret paradise.

episodes.name: Cooperative Calligraphy
episodes.overview: Annie's missing pen leads to friction within the group.

episodes.name: Conspiracy Theories and Interior Design
episodes.overview: When Jeff tries to obtain credit for a fictitious class, the unintended consequences rock Greendale. Abed and Troy build an elaborate blanket fort.

episodes.name: Mixology Certification
episodes.overview: Troy's friends help him celebrate his 21st birthday.

episodes.name: Abed's Uncontrollable Christmas
episodes.overview: The meaning of Christmas is lost and Abed's intense fixation on the holiday concerns the group in this special stop-motion animation episode.

episodes.name: Asian Population Studies
episodes.overview: With Chang pressing for membership in the study group, Annie's latest crush has Jeff reeling as Shirley unveils some stunning news.

episodes.name: Celebrity Pharmacology
episodes.overview: Pierce's efforts to bribe director Annie may undermine the theater group's antidrug play; Jeff's texting prank puts Britta in an awkward situation.

episodes.name: Advanced Dungeons & Dragons
episodes.overview: Abed invites "Fat Neil" to play a game of Dungeons & Dragons with the rest of the study group, hoping to boost his confidence, after Jeff becomes concerned about him being a loner. When Pierce finds out he was not invited, he joins anyway, disrupting their plans.

episodes.name: Early 21st Century Romanticism
episodes.overview: On Valentine's Day, Troy and Abed compete for the attention of an assistant librarian, while Britta tries to show she's open-minded about lesbians.

episodes.name: Intermediate Documentary Filmmaking
episodes.overview: Claiming that he is about to die, Pierce summons the study group to the hospital to bequeath his belongings to them.

episodes.name: Intro to Political Science
episodes.overview: For an upcoming vice-presidential visit, Glendale's Dean Pelton hastily organizes an election for student body president that pits Annie against Jeff.

episodes.name: Custody Law and Eastern European Diplomacy
episodes.overview: Although Shirley and Andre don't want Chang involved with her baby, he resolves to be a good dad. Abed and Troy's new friend may be a war criminal.

episodes.name: Critical Film Studies
episodes.overview: Jeff and the group arrange a Pulp Fiction birthday party for Abed, but he has his own plans, starting with an expensive dinner for himself and Jeff.

episodes.name: Competitive Wine Tasting
episodes.overview: Jeff is suspicious of Pierce's engagement to a pretty classmate. Troy invents a childhood trauma to impress Britta, and Abed challenges a professor.

episodes.name: Paradigms of Human Memory
episodes.overview: Working on their final anthropology diorama, Chang finds a cache of items stolen by Troy's monkey that dredge up unhappy memories for the study group.

episodes.name: Applied Anthropology and Culinary Arts
episodes.overview: As the semester ends, the anthropology final is disrupted when Shirley goes into labor and her husband, Andre, is summoned to school for the birth.

episodes.name: A Fistful of Paintballs (1)
episodes.overview: A $100,000 paintball war prize pits members of the study group against one another, until they decide to join forces to stop a mysterious challenger.

episodes.name: For a Few Paintballs More (2)
episodes.overview: As the paintball war is revealed to be a City College plot, Jeff and Troy vie for control of Greendale's ragtag army, while Pierce betrays the group.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: The misfits of Greendale Community College return for more wacky lessons in love, life and friendship in the second season of this ensemble sitcom.

episodes.name: Biology 101
episodes.overview: As Jeff tries to keep Pierce from rejoining the study group, Dean Pelton faces off with Vice Dean Laybourne for control of Greendale.

episodes.name: Geography of Global Conflict
episodes.overview: As Annie competes with an overachieving rival in a Model United Nations competition, Jeff wrestles with his feelings for his ambitious friend.

episodes.name: Competitive Ecology
episodes.overview: The study group struggles to incorporate a fellow classmate while working on a project for Professor Kane's class.

episodes.name: Remedial Chaos Theory
episodes.overview: When Jeff introduces an element of randomness into Troy and Abed's housewarming party, reality splits into six timelines.

episodes.name: Horror Fiction in Seven Spooky Steps
episodes.overview: When a personality test suggests that one group member is a homicidal maniac, they use a series of scary Halloween stories to expose the killer.

episodes.name: Advanced Gay
episodes.overview: When a drag queen's song makes Hawthorne Wipes an iconic gay product, Pierce embraces it, until his homophobic dad shows up to squelch the idea.

episodes.name: Studies in Modern Movement
episodes.overview: Annie has second thoughts about moving in with Troy and Abed once she realizes that they expect her to live in a blanket fort.

episodes.name: Documentary Filmmaking: Redux
episodes.overview: As Dean Pelton films a new commercial for Greendale, the production takes a wild turn once he discovers that a famous alum has agreed to appear in it.

episodes.name: Foosball and Nocturnal Vigilantism
episodes.overview: When Shirley agrees to coach Jeff in foosball, they realize that she bullied him mercilessly when they were kids.

episodes.name: Regional Holiday Music
episodes.overview: The study group is slowly convinced to fill in for the Glee Club at Greendale's Christmas pageant.

episodes.name: Urban Matrimony and the Sandwich Arts
episodes.overview: When Shirley's remarriage to Andre threatens to put her dreams of starting a business with Pierce on hold, Britta steps in.

episodes.name: Contemporary Impressionists
episodes.overview: The study group must work as celebrity impersonators at a bar mitzvah to pay off Abed's debt to a talent agency owner.

guest_stars.character: Christopher Walken Impersonator/ Tommy Lee Jones Impersonator
guest_stars.name: Jim Meskimen

episodes.name: Digital Exploration of Interior Design (1)
episodes.overview: When Britta falls for the human embodiment of the Subway sandwich chain, Shirley and Pierce hope to use the situation to their advantage.

episodes.name: Pillows and Blankets (2)
episodes.overview: The students of Greendale are drawn into an epic pillow fight as Troy and Abed start a war that threatens to destroy their unique friendship.

episodes.name: Origins of Vampire Mythology
episodes.overview: When a carnival comes to Greendale, Annie goes to great lengths to make sure that Britta doesn't contact her carnival worker ex-boyfriend.

episodes.name: Virtual Systems Analysis
episodes.overview: After sending Troy and Britta on a date, Annie volunteers to keep Abed company in his Dreamatorium.

episodes.name: Basic Lupine Urology
episodes.overview: When the yam the study group was growing for biology class is killed, Troy and Abed are on the case.

episodes.name: Course Listing Unavailable
episodes.overview: After a classmate suddenly dies, the study group decides to host a memorial, but Jeff turns his speech into an angry anti-Greendale rant.

episodes.name: Curriculum Unavailable
episodes.overview: After Abed is caught trespassing at Greendale, he and his friends visit a psychiatrist.

episodes.name: Digital Estate Planning
episodes.overview: Pierce and his closest friends are summoned to Hawthorne Labs to play a video game that will determine who will inherit his father's fortune.

episodes.name: The First Chang Dynasty
episodes.overview: The study group stages an elaborate heist to break in to Greendale and free Dean Pelton from the clutches of Chang.

episodes.name: Introduction to Finality
episodes.overview: Jeff agrees to represent Shirley in a case against Pierce to determine official ownership of their new sandwich shop.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: The motley gang of eccentrics anchored by disbarred lawyer Jeff Winger is back for another season of learning in this sardonic comedy series.

episodes.name: History 101
episodes.overview: Jeff agrees to represent Shirley in a case against Pierce to determine official ownership of their new sandwich shop.

episodes.name: Paranormal Parentage
episodes.overview: On the way to a Halloween party, the study group must free Pierce from his panic room and slowly comes to suspect that his mansion is haunted.

episodes.name: Conventions of Space and Time
episodes.overview: Troy worries about losing Abed to a fellow Inspector Spacetime fan at a convention for the show, while Annie fantasizes about being married to Jeff.

episodes.name: Alternative History of the German Invasion
episodes.overview: The study group contends with a group of German students who take over the study room. Chang makes his return to campus.

episodes.name: Cooperative Escapism in Familial Relations
episodes.overview: Britta joins Jeff to see his estranged father on Thanksgiving. Shirley invites the rest of the group to spend the holiday with her judgmental in-laws.

episodes.name: Advanced Documentary Filmmaking
episodes.overview: Greendale comes together to get to the bottom of Chang's amnesia, which Abed films as a documentary. Jeff, however, suspects Chang is faking it.

episodes.name: Economics of Marine Biology
episodes.overview: Dean Pelton enlists the study group to beautify the campus to woo a wealthy student to Greendale. A class on teaching P.E. pits Shirley against Troy.

episodes.name: Herstory of Dance
episodes.overview: Jeff sets out to embarrass Britta when she announces a dance for women's empowerment. Abed dreams of shuttling between two dates in one night.

episodes.name: Intro to Felt Surrogacy
episodes.overview: Dean Pelton prompts the study group to use puppets to relive the traumatic events of a recent adventure.

episodes.name: Intro to Knots
episodes.overview: Jeff organizes a lovely holiday gathering at his apartment, but Annie secretly invites Professor Cornwallis to get in his good graces.

episodes.name: Basic Human Anatomy
episodes.overview: When Annie and Shirley learn that Leonard is actually holding the spot as the class valedictorian, they join forces to bring him down.

episodes.name: Heroic Origins
episodes.overview: Abed's research into the study group's history uncovers an overlooked series of chance encounters that led each of them to Greendale.

episodes.name: Advanced Introduction to Finality
episodes.overview: A plan to celebrate Jeff's early graduation is unexpectedly disrupted by the study group's evil doppelgangers from the Darkest Timeline.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: Greendale Community College continues to attract an odd assortment of intellectual "seekers" in the fourth season of this sardonic sitcom.

episodes.name: Repilot
episodes.overview: With his law practice doomed, Jeff returns to Greendale to start a class action suit against the school, but a hologram of Pierce has him reconsider.

episodes.name: Introduction to Teaching
episodes.overview: Abed tackles a two-day crash course on Nicolas Cage, while a clueless Jeff begins his teaching career with Annie as his most demanding student.

episodes.name: Basic Intergluteal Numismatics
episodes.overview: With the mysterious Ass Crack Bandit back at Greendale, Annie and Jeff are on the case. As clues and suspicions mount, Shirley delivers shocking news.

episodes.name: Cooperative Polygraphy
episodes.overview: Pierce's funeral leaves the study group with mixed feelings, especially after their late tormentor leaves one last test to reveal everyone's secrets.

episodes.name: Geothermal Escapism
episodes.overview: For Troy's last day at Greendale, Abed holds a campus-wide "hot lava" fantasy game. With a comic book worth $50,000 as the prize, it's an all-out war.

episodes.name: Analysis of Cork-Based Networking
episodes.overview: While Annie and Hickey's fight to get a bulletin board repaired spirals out of control, Abed and Britta go to war over spoilers of his favorite show.

episodes.name: Bondage and Beta Male Sexuality
episodes.overview: Jeff counsels a smitten Duncan on how to get a date with Britta but is developing feelings of his own. An angry Hickey tries to teach Abed a lesson.

episodes.name: App Development and Condiments
episodes.overview: A new caste system takes over when Greendale beta tests an app that ranks everyone. Shirley loves her new status, but Jeff and Britta want it stopped.

episodes.name: VCR Maintenance and Educational Publishing
episodes.overview: Abed and Annie try to solve their new roommate dilemma with a retro VCR game, while Jeff, Shirley and Hickey hatch a plan to sell stolen textbooks.

episodes.name: Advanced Advanced Dungeons & Dragons
episodes.overview: To help Hickey be a more involved grandfather, which means patching up a bad relationship with his son, the gang creates an epic role-playing game.

episodes.name: G.I. Jeff
episodes.overview: Jeff's depression over turning 40 leads him to drink himself unconscious. In his dreams, he and the gang are part of the "G. I. Joe" cartoon team.

episodes.name: Basic Story
episodes.overview: The Save Greendale Committee's success is short-lived when the board votes for a corporate sellout, but Pelton, Annie and Abed might find a solution.

episodes.name: Basic Sandwich
episodes.overview: To save Greendale from being sold, the gang searches for an eccentric computer science professor's legendary treasure hidden beneath the school.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: Attorney Jeff Winger and his wacky study group are assailed by new academic and life challenges in the fifth season of this mischievous sitcom.

episodes.name: Ladders
episodes.overview: New administrative consultant Frankie's strict — and sobering — changes split the group when Abed goes rogue to side with the enemy.

episodes.name: Lawnmower Maintenance and Postnatal Care
episodes.overview: When Dean Pelton loses himself — and a chunk of the college budget — in a virtual reality system, Jeff seeks help from its cantankerous inventor.

episodes.name: Basic Crisis Room Decorum
episodes.overview: A rival's attack ad puts the group into defensive mode — and a moral quandary. Britta and Chang find new ways to gross everyone out.

episodes.name: Queer Studies & Advanced Waxing
episodes.overview: Dean Pelton's sexuality gives him an uncomfortable edge for a school board seat. Chang scores a surprise win in a stage adaptation of "The Karate Kid."

episodes.name: Laws of Robotics and Party Rights
episodes.overview: When prisoners roll into Greendale via telerobot, Jeff meets his match in a clever convict. Britta's plans for a raging house party backfire.

episodes.name: Basic Email Security
episodes.overview: A hacker angry over a racist comic's planned campus performance threatens to publish the activity committee's personal emails.

episodes.name: Advanced Safety Features
episodes.overview: Britta's ex-boyfriend, Rick, returns, reigniting her far-fetched dreams of a normal relationship. Annie goes to extremes to win Elroy over.

episodes.name: Intro to Recycled Cinema
episodes.overview: A commercial catchphrase catapults Chang to viral fame and a life-changing move. The group bands together to make movie magic for Abed.

episodes.name: Grifting 101
episodes.overview: Visiting Professor DeSalvo gives Jeff and his friends a master class in grifting and a bonus lesson on the art of revenge.

episodes.name: Basic RV Repair and Palmistry
episodes.overview: A 19-foot plaster hand guides the group on an emotional journey as they travel through mountains and flashbacks while aboard Elroy's RV.

episodes.name: Modern Espionage
episodes.overview: Heroes are born, promises are broken and the stakes are raised when paintball makes an explosive return to Greendale's campus.

episodes.name: Wedding Videography
episodes.overview: When two Greendale students get married, the wedding reception takes a turn after Jeff unwittingly exposes an inconvenient truth.

episodes.name: Emotional Consequences of Broadcast Television
episodes.overview: The former study group's future — and friendships — are put to a test when one chapter of their lives closes and a new one begins.

6.name: Season 6
6.overview: Greendale's best worst former study group learns lessons in life and the chemistry of weirdness as it graduates to a momentous ending. Maybe.
